{"tid":745911,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Non-Steam/Steam] CS1.6 Multian 多模式Server (BB/DeathRun/ZP)","createTime":"2018-07-17T07:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T09:45:22.000Z","uid":9191,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"440a3521055bfbfbca02e62120b2b150eff4cda9","tid":745911,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"IP: 66.42.50.83:27015<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.gametracker.com/server_info/66.42.50.83:27015/b_560_95_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.gametracker.com%2Fserver_info%2F66.42.50.83%3A27015%2Fb_560_95_1.png&h=f38db679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>基本指令：</strong><br />\n/reg - 以目前Player ID註冊/開啟自動登入<br />\nrtv - 投票轉場<br />\nnom bb - 提名Base Builder 6.5模式地圖<br />\nnom deathrun - 提名DeathRun模式地圖<br />\nnom zm - 提名Zombie Plague 5.0模式地圖<br />\nvoteban - 投票封禁<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Base Builder 6.5 指令：</strong><br />\nbind &lt;key&gt; +use (後台) - 移動可用版塊指令<br />\n+use + right click - 將目前版塊推遠<br />\n+use + left click - 將目前版塊拉近<br />\nm - 選擇喪屍類型 (選擇後自動respawn)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Zombie Plague 5.0 指令：</strong><br />\n/bank - 查看帳號現有ammo pack<br />\ndeposit &lt;amount&gt; - 將指定數目ammo pack存入 <br />\ndeposit all - 將全部ammo pack存入<br />\nwithdraw &lt;amount&gt; - 將指定數目ammo pack提出<br />\nwithdraw all - 將全部ammo pack提出<br />\n<br />\nZombie Plague 5.0 每次離開Server都會將目前所有ammo pack直接存入 <br />\n下次進入嘅時候如果想拎返出嚟就用withdraw指令<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主要Server File下載：(包含Zombie Plague, Base Builder及DeathRun基本模組/音效/地圖)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/multiancstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fmultiancstrike&d=YXRUfOKYuqTA9jvC%2Bdoc5cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8b3a4ba2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/multiancstrike</a>"},{"pid":"1e1e631acfaa5734dc9725df1b1a12b5fdded1dd","tid":745911,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass